Commentary Text: Jordan to Rayudu, out Caught by Arshdeep Singh!! Rayudu is distraught! Commentary Text: Thakur to Mayank, out Lbw!! Given out lbw and Mayank Agarwal decides not to review. He had a brief chat with his skipper who might have prompted him against the review. Was that sliding down leg? Mayank walked across and looked to flick this into the fine leg fence, the ball wobbles in from a fullish length and raps him in line with middle and leg. It looked to be skipping down leg to the naked eye and the replays reveal that it's missing leg. Oh dear. Mayank lbw b Thakur 12(12) [4s-2]
